node.text:
Where there is light there is shadow. Two Elements creatively studies and used for centuries by artists to add drama and life to their creations. 

Artwork by: 
Nilo Badajos and Teody Racuya 

#chiaroscuros #artph #artgallery #lightandshadow

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Art Circle gallery on March 22, 2022. May be art of 6 people, outdoors and text that says 'ART CIRCLE GALLERY CHIAROSCUROS The Interplay of light and shadow Nilo Badajos Lemuel Cunanan Roger Crisostomo Teody Racuya MARCH 18 to 28, 2022 4L ART CENTER SM MEGAMALL'.

node.text:
Art Circle Gallery is proud to feature the works of Nilo Badajos, Lemuel Cunanan, Roger Crisostomo and Teody Racuya in a group art exhibition that highlights the different methods from Tenebrism to Sfumato whilst paying tribute to our local scenery.

#artgallery #chiaroscuros #artph #lightandshadow

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Art Circle gallery on March 22, 2022. May be art of 8 people and outdoors.

node.text:
This technique was popularized by Leonardo De Vinci when he discovered that volume could be achieved by gradually playing with dark and light tones and popularized by Caravaggio and gave birth to many classic pieces of art we come to know today.

Artwork by: 
Lemuel Cunanan & Roger Crisostomo

#artgallery #chiaroscuros #artph #lightandshadow
